    public class PersonEditor
extends KSJInternalFrame
implements javax.swing.event.ListSelectionListener
    The PersonEditor is a window that displays an Individual's fields for editing. It is an extension of KSJInternalFrame so it will appear in the View menu.

    NOTE: Those exception texts intended for debugging are not translated.
